165
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,920
then it's said to be linearly dependent on it.

166
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,920
The dimension of a vector space is very simple.

167
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:33,920
It's the maximum number of linearly independent vectors

168
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,920
