00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:39,920
So the property is characterized

826
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:42,920
by an operator and an eigenvalue.

827
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:44,920
Okay?

828
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,920
A projection operator

829
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:50,920
is a tool for calculating the probability

